She thinks it's due to
your magic presence.

01:51:13.372 --> 01:51:15.798
Oh my! I didn't know

01:51:16.685 --> 01:51:18.045
that I had such powers of healing.

01:51:25.978 --> 01:51:27.886
There's something
she wants from you.

01:51:33.142 --> 01:51:34.148
What?

01:51:34.805 --> 01:51:35.928
An autograph.

01:51:40.121 --> 01:51:41.412
Have you got a notebook?

01:51:44.068 --> 01:51:45.068
No?

01:51:46.080 --> 01:51:47.086
Okay, wait.

01:52:05.423 --> 01:52:06.798
May I just borrow your pen?

01:52:11.689 --> 01:52:12.693
Thank you.

01:52:16.223 --> 01:52:17.229
What's your name?

01:52:19.173 --> 01:52:20.197
Sairinidhri.

01:52:24.115 --> 01:52:25.121
Bulbul.

01:52:56.783 --> 01:52:57.810
How are you?

01:53:05.193 --> 01:53:06.227
You know everything.

01:53:07.671 --> 01:53:08.677
You tell me.

01:53:10.283 --> 01:53:11.298
Fine.

01:53:15.537 --> 01:53:16.542
Why not?

01:53:19.818 --> 01:53:22.146
I feel ass if

01:53:23.692 --> 01:53:25.331
there is some void.

01:53:27.320 --> 01:53:28.607
I'm missing something.

01:53:29.427 --> 01:53:31.343
Really? Why?

01:53:35.142 --> 01:53:36.615
I don't suppose we'll meet again.

01:53:40.287 --> 01:53:41.893
And you are not
likely to get into films.

01:53:42.294 --> 01:53:44.834
No. You live in a different world.

01:53:46.102 --> 01:53:49.369
We're out on the streets,
in trams and buses.

01:53:50.714 --> 01:53:52.360
If three of my films flop in a row,

01:53:54.391 --> 01:53:56.006
I might go back into that world.

01:53:56.806 --> 01:53:57.833
Don't say that.

01:53:58.240 --> 01:54:01.252
I'm sure you'll stay right where
you are, for a long time yet.

01:54:02.373 --> 01:54:04.713
I'm sure you'll have
a huge fan following.

01:54:09.574 --> 01:54:11.328
Your interview...

01:54:20.825 --> 01:54:22.199
Why did you tear it up?

01:54:32.458 --> 01:54:33.790
Will you write from memory?

01:54:38.324 --> 01:54:40.073
I'll keep it in my memory.

01:54:45.580 --> 01:54:46.594
I'll leave now.

01:54:48.412 --> 01:54:49.419
Goodbye.

01:55:37.085 --> 01:55:39.354
'The train to Amritsar...'

01:55:41.848 --> 01:55:44.079
'At 12:50...'